*& Refactoring Notes:                                                       *
*&   - Removed dependency on Dynpro screens (100, 200)                      *
*&   - Replaced CL_GUI_CUSTOM_CONTAINER with CL_GUI_DOCKING_CONTAINER       *
*&   - Replaced CHMOD screen with CL_GUI_DIALOGBOX_CONTAINER                *
*&   - Added Microsoft logo header using CL_GUI_PICTURE                     *
*&   - All original functionality preserved                                 *
