*&--------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Original Version History (from S. Hermann):                              *
*&--------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*&--------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Features:                                                                *
*&   - Navigate in remote folders with graphic interface                    *
*&   - Sort & filter remote file/folder listings                            *
*&   - Open remote file with default application or text editor             *
*&   - Upload/download files by button or drag & drop                       *
*&   - Manage file and folder (create, rename, remove, copy, move)          *
*&   - Open server shortcut & path from clipboard                           *
*&   - Manage server shortcuts (create & delete)                            *
*&   - Copy path (server/local) to clipboard                                *
*&   - Compress remote file (TAR+BZ2 on Unix, ZIP on Windows)               *
*&   - Uncompress remote file (ZIP, TAR, GZ, BZ2)                           *
*&   - CHMOD on file/folder (Unix) / ATTRIB (Windows)                       *
*&   - Access to remote server //servername/path/                           *
*&--------------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Technical Notes:                                                         *
*&   - Runs without dynpro using CL_GUI_DOCKING_CONTAINER                   *
*&   - Designed for Windows local PC and Unix/Linux or Windows server       *
*&   - Uses shared memory to remember last used folders                     *
*&--------------------------------------------------------------------------*
REPORT zapp_server.

INCLUDE zapp_top.
INCLUDE zapp_cls.
INCLUDE zapp_sub.

START-OF-SELECTION.
  PERFORM init_auth.
  PERFORM init_screen.
  PERFORM write.
